{
  "stem": "5328.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because he wasn't home, my brother left by himself, and we remained.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a few days later, my father was walking about 50 miles, walking home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the way to walk home, he-- a German drunk fella-- man, soldier, recognized that he's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was very drunk, and he gave him a shovel to make his own grave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was making his own grave, and he stood by with him, with  that gun in his hand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, Jew, you make your own grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And soon he digged all the grave out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He give him a-- he slapped him with the shovel, and he said, run, Jew run!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the way he survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he came back to home, to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, everybody-- everybody-- anybody that want to go to Russia was-- the Russian open up the doors-- come, come to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Run away.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody thought that it's that bad, that it will be the that bad that we have to leave the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many people did leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because hearing what's going on, he was afraid of the German occupation, and he ran away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, he was working in a-- in a-- from the job, they ask him-- they ask everybody, you want to come with us to Russia?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he just picked up and went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we couldn't go, because the father wasn't home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not a jail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- he was sent away in a different city to work, not to be in the same city with his family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The court-- I mean, from court.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a court, and this was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His punishment.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The civil court.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the punishment.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
